devdoc.author: Compound

getBorrowRate(address,uint256,uint256).details: The return value should be scaled by 1e18, thus a return value of     `(true, 1000000000000)` implies an interest rate of 0.000001 or 0.0001% *per block*.

params._asset: The asset to get the interest rate of
params.borrows: The total borrows of the asset in the market
params.cash: The total cash of the asset in the market

getBorrowRate(address,uint256,uint256).return: Success or failure and the borrow interest rate per block scaled by 10e18

getSupplyRate(address,uint256,uint256).details: The return value should be scaled by 1e18, thus a return value of     `(true, 1000000000000)` implies an interest rate of 0.000001 or 0.0001% *per block*.

params._asset: The asset to get the interest rate of
params.borrows: The total borrows of the asset in the market
params.cash: The total cash of the asset in the market

getSupplyRate(address,uint256,uint256).return: Success or failure and the supply interest rate per block scaled by 10e18

devdoc.title: The Compound Standard Interest Rate Model

getBorrowRate(address,uint256,uint256).notice: Gets the current borrow interest rate based on the given asset, total cash and total borrows

getSupplyRate(address,uint256,uint256).notice: Gets the current supply interest rate based on the given asset, total cash and total borrows
